        <type>VLC_API int</type>
        <definition>VLC_API int vlc_mwait_i11e</definition>
        <argsstring>(vlc_tick_t)</argsstring>
        <name>vlc_mwait_i11e</name>
        <param>
          <type><ref refid="vlc__common_8h_1a4185ff2b4df43e2bfd7ae9736b235d35" kindref="member">vlc_tick_t</ref></type>
        </param>
        <briefdescription>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Interruptible variant of mwait().</para>
<para>Waits for a specified timestamp or, if the calling thread has an interruption context, an interruption.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="return"><para>EINTR if an interruption occurred, otherwise 0 once the timestamp is reached. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
